{"word":"πάγκλαυστος","slug":"πάγκλαυστος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πάγκλαυστος</b></el> <el>(πάγκλαυστος, ορ <el>-κλαυτος, ον</el>,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κλαίω'><el>κλαίω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>all-lamented, most lamentable</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>all tearful</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}